<p>Andy runs <a href="http://stuffandnonsense.co.uk" title="Stuff And Nonsense">Stuff and Nonsense</a>, a small website design studio based in North Wales which has made a big name for itself by designing fantastic websites. Besides being behind <a href="http://www.stuffandnonsense.co.uk/projects/320andup/" title="320 and Up">320 and Up</a>, Andy writes books, including <i>Transcending CSS</i> and the acclaimed <i><a href="http://hardboiledwebdesign.com" title="Hardboiled Web Design">Hardboiled Web Design</a></i>. Andy shares his passion for amazing web design through articles and at workshops and conferences all over the world.</p>
<p>He tweets as <a href="http://twitter.com/#!/malarkey" title="Andy's Twitter Account">@malarkey</a>.</p>